KTN News unveils its new team of young, accountable and energetic news anchors. The team consists of three beautiful ladies and one gentleman. The new faces are Brenda Czeda Radido, Maalika Kazia, Frida Mwaka and Jesse Rogers. The new anchors will be gracing your TV screens as from today with breaking news, live coverage and credible news from Kenya, across Africa and the world. They are expected to inject fresh blood to the already dedicated news team giving you more in-depth reporting, and as the saying goes knowledge is power. Avoid becoming a victim of Fake News. Subscribe to the Standard Group SMS service by texting 'NEWS' to 22840.